BA_ "Description" SG_ 2189468929 ECSIVSS_FLWhlVrtclAccelSnsrVal "Wheel Vertical Acceleration Sensor - FL
0x0000~0x03FF:-13.3g(102)~13.3g(921)/0x0400~0x0FFE:Not used/0x0FFF:Invalid

 /* Wheel G value, 102:-13.3g, 921 : +13.3g */
Value : 102(-13.3G) ~ 921(+13.3G)
If Value <= 102, Then Value = -13.3g
If Value >= 92";
