BA_ "Description" SG_ 2328016132 VCU_AvnDteCorFacVal "AVN DTE Correlation Factor Value
- 0xFF : 255 (Invalid)
- 0x0~0xC8 : 0~200
- 0xC8~0xFE : 201~254 (Reserved)
- Physical value min. : 0 * 0.01 = 0 (0x0)
- Physical value max. : 200 * 0.01 = 2 (0xC8)";
