BA_ "Description" SG_ 2328016132 VCU_DteGuidePosVal "DTE Guide Position Value
- 0x7F : 127 (Invalid)
- 0x0~0x78 : 0~120
- 0x79~0x7E : 121~126 (Reserved)
- Physical value min. : 0 -10 = -10 (0x0)
- Physical value max. : 120 - 10 = 110 (0x78)";
