BA_ "Description" SG_ 2223056129 SAS_AnglVal "Information regarding the steering wheel angle.  (PH) = (HEX) * 0.1 (0 <  HEX < 7FFFH) or (PH) = (HEX - 65536) * 0.1 (HEX > 7FFFH)

