BA_ "Description" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_Crc2Val "The data area for CRC calculation is based on the data length (DLC) of the message DB.
The CRC shall be calculated over the entire data block (excluding the CRC bytes) including the user data, alive counter and Data ID

- CRC Polynomial (0x1021) , Ini";
