BA_ "Description" SG_ 2151682049 ACU_CrshInfo "1)When crash output is issued, this signal is transmitted as 0x2. 
2)When crash output is not issued and ACU meets MCB requirement of ESC.  this signal is transmitted as 0x1.

Just then If ACU receives feedback signal from ESC this signal is transmitt";
